e":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:47:08.000Z","msg":"如果企業債券幾千蚊就入到場嘅話,大部份公司根本唔需要俾咁高息出黎<br />\n因為一般人問銀行借少少錢,利息都已經低至 2-3%<br />\n公司發債最大嘅目的係籌到足夠size嘅錢<br />\n入場門檻高可以減少好多admin cost同確保筆錢嘅份量<br />\n<br />\n債券基金係買一大堆公司嘅債,定期派返債息出黎或者繼續留喺基金入面滾存<br />\n同買直債嘅模式好唔同<br />\n因為直債hold to maturity就已經直接拎到當初預期嘅回報率(yield)<br />\n可以避免到期想拎錢嘅時候價格有較大波動<br />\n<br />\n如果資金未夠你去private bank到玩<br />\n可以Through iFast去買,基本嘅選擇可以喺Bondsupermart入面睇到<br />\n而且平台入面可以買到IPO嘅債<br />\n不過大部份債係USD 200k入場,都有少部份係USD100k 入場"},{"pid":"c384295b68f73139a70857e3043b1626b64300a3","tid":399343,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你想問債券基金？</blockquote><br />\n似似哋香港有冇</blockquote><br />\n債基唔同債卷, 唔好撈亂<br />\n香港銀行知債卷冇肉食, 私銀先有得買<br />\n債基我就唔建議大家買喇, 伏黎, 自己做Research</blockquote><br />\n債基係唔同債券組成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買債券個刻我計到yield同幾時收番本金<br />\n<br />\n但債基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e599acf7eaa1fff331284da77821616116e7fa5","tid":399343,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fr0vq2i4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffr0vq2i4&h=12f3541e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實唔難"},{"pid":"19428be2a603f2876acf4250d469efb969a2b6b9","tid":399343,"uid":44202,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要成兩百萬, 有冇低入場費版？例如幾皮</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b192497590753e1ed78e628e2488d92b07ef79d5","tid":399343,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你想問債券基金？</blockquote><br />\n似似哋香港有冇</blockquote><br />\n債基唔同債卷, 唔好撈亂<br />\n香港銀行知債卷冇肉食, 私銀先有得買<br />\n債基我就唔建議大家買喇, 伏黎, 自己做Research</blockquote><br />\n債基係唔同債券組成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買債券個刻我計到yield同幾時收番本金<br />\n<br />\n但債基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買債基計計就知伏<br />\naaa小過3%你減返乜費物費<br />\n佢要渣幾多垃圾債你先有肉食"},{"pid":"d979c84a96f4725750d96d6f697b0d8c4eacd6f5","tid":399343,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"買BND咪得"},{"pid":"a2579af28fa49cbdaaa0f644a0d82ee16b08bf8c","tid":399343,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T05:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買BND咪得</blockquote><br />\n計埋税得1.x%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338a0a14559c4e4aa439fac669f316013e11a9de","tid":399343,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"請問強積金內可選嘅債券基金同市面上可以買到嘅都係一樣？"},{"pid":"14ab41ea5ed916da0cc0ddbcdc3bf3c5e0dec216","tid":399343,"uid":13879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"買基金咪俾人分咗利瀾"}]}